Class Test2_UI

  • java.lang.Object
    • java.awt.Component
      • java.awt.Container
        • javax.swing.JComponent
          • javax.swing.JPanel
            • P6.Test2_UI
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.awt.image.ImageObserver, java.awt.MenuContainer, java.io.Serializable, javax.accessibility.Accessible

    public class Test2_UI
extends javax.swing.JPanel
    This class creates a graphic environment that contains a numerous of different J-components. The class contains 49 JLabel-components that shows the values who is stored in a Array7x7-object. In this class you have the options to move the array7x7 to the left and right where the values is in the JTextField-components and later stored in the Array7x7.
